snippet.title: The Tale of Food ★ Global Server Debut PV!
snippet.description:
Food personified into Food Souls, adventure with them across time and space, together to create our exclusive memories!

「Heartwarming story preserved in one bite!😋」

The much-anticipated Food Personified Story RPG -The Tale of Food, will be released soon!
